				<div class="bbcode_postedby">
					<img src="images/misc/quote_icon.png" alt="Quote" /> Originally Posted by <strong>Zaes</strong>
					<a href="showthread.php?s=51cef6bd4de151b38bc5c786a2c41e76&amp;p=1845755#post1845755" rel="nofollow"><img class="inlineimg" src="images/buttons/viewpost-right.png" alt="View Post" /></a>
